ngFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">第</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">五</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">章&nbsp; 录取原则及毕业证发放</span></p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">第十</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">二</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">条</span>&nbsp;学校的招生录取工作严格按照《教育部关于做好2024年普通高校招生工作的通知》（教学〔2024〕2号）要求实施。全面贯彻实施高校招生“阳光工程”，坚持公平、公正、公开的原则，坚持德智体美劳全面考核、综合评价、择优录取。</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">第十</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">三</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">条</span>&nbsp;普通类专业录取，学校按考生的投档成绩和专业志愿，按“分数优先、遵循专业志愿”原则择优录取。对于考生专业志愿无法满足时，对服从专业调剂的考生，将由学校调剂到招生计划尚未完成的相关专业，对不服从专业调剂的考生，作退档处理。若考生投档分数相同，遵照生源省（自治区、直辖市）投档排序规则录取。</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">第十</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">四</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">条</span>&nbsp;学校在高考综合改革试点省（市、自治区），按其高考改革方案相关规定进行录取。同时将考生的综合素质评价信息作为录取的参考依据。按照院校专业组模式投档的省份，在考生所投档的专业组内，按照“分数优先、遵循专业志愿”的原则择优录取。</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">第十</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">五</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">条</span>&nbsp;学校艺体类专业文理兼收，不单独设立校考，美术类专业要求无色盲。承认生源所在省份统考或者联考成绩，按所在生源省份高考投档录取规则执行遵循生源地省级招生主管部门的投档原则，在进档的同类专业考生中依据投档成绩择优录取；如遇投档成绩相同，按高考文化成绩从高到低择优录取。</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">第十</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">六</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">条</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">&nbsp;</span>报考应用英语专业的考生限其参加全国统考的外语语种为英语，其他专业不限考生应试外语语种，但学校以英语作为基础外语安排教学。</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">第十</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">七</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">条</span>&nbsp;学校对各省（市、自治区）的优惠加分政策均按国家教育部及有关省份高考加分、降分政策执行，在录取时予以认可。</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">第十</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">八</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">条</span>&nbsp;对考生身体健康状况及身体条件的要求，除专业录取要求特别注明的专业外，原则上按《普通高等学校招生体检工作指导意见》及有关规定执行。</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">第十</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">九</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">条</span>&nbsp;毕业证发放：达到本科培养要求的毕业生，颁发江西软件职业技术大学全日制职业本科毕业文凭；符合学位授予条件者，授予相应的学士学位。达到专科培养要求的毕业生，颁发江西软件职业技术大学全日制普通专科毕业文凭。</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">第</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">六</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">章&nbsp; 新生入学及其他</span></p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">第</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">二十</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">条</span>&nbsp;已录取新生应按学校规定的时间和要求办理入学报到手续。已录取但不能按时报到者，须向学校提出书面申请，经同意后方可延期；未经批准逾期15天不报到者，视为自动放弃入学资格。</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">第</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">二十</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">一</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">条</span>&nbsp;新生入学后三个月内，学校按国家招生工作有关规定进行新生入学资格复查与身体复检。对复查(复检、复试)发现的问题，学校将集中研究处理，凡属舞弊者，一经查实，即取消其入学资格。对于弄虚作假情节严重或涉嫌冒名顶替上大学的，移送相关部门调查处理。</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">第二十</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">二</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">条</span>&nbsp;学校建立了奖、贷、助、勤、补等多元的资助制度。对于家庭经济困难的学生，可申请生源地助学贷款和通过国家奖助学金申请、勤工助学、特困补助等措施完成学业，对特别优秀的学生给予全额奖学金。</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">第二十</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">三</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">条</span>&nbsp;退学退费办法：若学生入学后提出退学退费申请的，我校严格按照江西省教育厅《江西省民办高校学生退学退费办法》的规定，办理退学退费手续。</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">第</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">七</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">章&nbsp; 招生咨询及联系方式</span></p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">第二十</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">四</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">条</span>&nbsp;学校招生咨询部门：招生办。</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap;">招生咨询电话：0791-83792888、83792998（传真）</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap;">学校网址：http://www.jxuspt.com/</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap;">招生信息网：http://zhaosheng.jxuspt.com/</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap;">官方微信公众号：ahead-edu</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap;">监督部门：江西软件职业技术大学纪检监察室</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap;">监督电话：0791-83792051</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap;">举报邮箱：604555405@qq.com</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">第八章 附件</span></p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">第二十</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">五</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">条</span>&nbsp;学校招生工作严格落实教育部关于信息公开的相关要求，所有招生政策、招生章程、招生计划、收费标准、录取程序、录取结果、重大事件违规处理结果等信息，在学校招生官网公开。</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">第二十</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">六</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">条</span>&nbsp;我校未委托任何中介机构或个人进行高考招生录取工作，对以学校名义进行非法招生宣传和招生录取等活动的中介机构或个人，学校保留依法追究其责任的权利。</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">第二十</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">七</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">条</span>&nbsp;本章程适用于江西软件职业技术大学全日制统招本、专科招生工作，由学校招生办负责解释。</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">第二十</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">八</span><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">条</span>&nbsp;本章程自公布之日起施行。</p><p><br/></p>